SYNOPSIS: Yoga for Well Being contains three short yoga sequences; RESTFUL SLEEP [RUN-TIME 00:19:35] Sleep better with a practice of soothing hip openers, forward bends and restorative poses that will prepare you for a better night's sleep. GREATER ENERGY [RUN-TIME 00:20:16] Invigorate your body with a practice of revitalizing standing poses and shoulder openers to awaken your body and revive your energy. MENTAL CLARITY [RUN-TIME 00:20:41] Clear your mind with a practice of quieting forward bends, twists and balancing poses to restore mental focus and clarity.
